sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Runner as GitHub Actions Runner<br/>(ephemeral, ~5 min)
    participant GitHub as GitHub OIDC Issuer<br/>token.actions.githubusercontent.com
    participant STS as GCP Security Token Service<br/>sts.googleapis.com
    participant IAM as GCP IAM Credentials<br/>iamcredentials.googleapis.com
    participant API as GCP APIs<br/>(Artifact Registry, GKE)

    Runner->>GitHub: Mint OIDC JWT for audience=<WIF provider>
    GitHub-->>Runner: Signed JWT<br/>{repository, ref, sha, sub, exp ~5min}
    Runner->>STS: Exchange JWT for federated token
    STS->>GitHub: Fetch JWKS, verify signature
    STS->>STS: Evaluate attribute_condition<br/>assertion.repository == "huchka/feedforge"
    STS-->>Runner: Federated access token
    Runner->>IAM: Impersonate service account<br/>(generateAccessToken)
    IAM->>IAM: Check workloadIdentityUser binding<br/>on principalSet
    IAM-->>Runner: GCP access token<br/>(SA identity, ~1 hour TTL)
    Runner->>API: Push image / kubectl apply<br/>using SA access token
